<seg id="853">"" "" "" "with this KIPI module, you can import or convert your imagery stored in RAW format into one of three formats JPEG, TIFF or PPM." "" "" ""</seg>
<seg id="854">The conversion is based on the command-line tool dcraw from Dave Coffin. an original quote from it is: do not expect dcraw to produce the same results as the software from your camera manufacturer. sometimes you get better results with dcraw.</seg>
<seg id="855">"" "" "" "first, select the RAW file that is to be converted and start the module. the Raw Image Converter window will then appear in mode for a single image." "" "" ""</seg>
